{"tid":314570,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"東方海外賣盤","createTime":"2017-07-09T10:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T08:13:21.000Z","uid":6582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec40a9a3294770ea453f680725a2e1879e535359","tid":314570,"uid":6582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"前特首董建華之父董浩雲創辦的香港最大航企東方海外（316）刊出通告，指獲中國遠洋提出全面收購東方海外國際的所有已發行股份，收購總代價為492億元，即每股78.67元，溢價較上周最後收市價高31%。董建華家族現時持東方海外約68%，董家已承諾賣股，涉資338億元。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自今年初起，市場不停傳出東方海外有賣盤消息，不過該公司卻不斷否認。東方海外年初至今股價已升近1倍，周五收市報60元。<br />\n<br />\n收購完成前必須符合幾大條件，包括符合中國《反壟斷法》。"},{"pid":"95ecfb3cbaa6e49a312a80d4e28c8418e0e142a8","tid":314570,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94eb2347431a350ed28e22ea71102130f174197b","tid":314570,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"完成歷史任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dc57628f5736e0ecb4f54b2362eb76458bf978","tid":314570,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:07:49.000Z","msg":"賣港賣咗三百幾億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2669aa1d083fdcc96b5f937d85401cc7cbf9ddd0","tid":314570,"uid":54486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"賣祖業，老豆係棺材彈出黎"},{"pid":"0bf2d925949a6bcbe60a970fc474a32773a7f781","tid":314570,"uid":17155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:40:52.000Z","msg":"星期五放晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63b00febade453bb204e820712916e6b90a1a79","tid":314570,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:42:15.000Z","msg":"家族生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel